videos.description: Marcquise Reed deflects a pass, which leads to a quick dunk by Gabe DeVoe, forcing coach Jim Boeheim to immediately call a timeout.
videos.headline: DeVoe gets on board quickly for Clemson

videos.description: Aamir Simms knocks down an elbow jump shot to end a 10-minute period without a field goal by both Clemson and Syracuse.
videos.headline: Jumper snaps Clemson's field-goal drought

videos.description: Marek Dolezaj takes the contact and makes a jumper for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Dolezaj gets and-1 bucket

videos.description: Tyus Battle gets into the lane and drains the game-tying basket for his 1,000th career point.
videos.headline: Battle eclipses 1,000 points as a sophomore

videos.description: Paschal Chukwu blocks a shot in transition, falls and gets back up to block another shot into the stands.
videos.headline: Chukwu denies access at rim twice

videos.description: Marcquise Reed beats a defender upcourt to finish a layup to bring Clemson within two points with less than a minute remaining.
videos.headline: Reed brings Clemson within 2

videos.description: Oshae Brissett gets up for a huge block on Marcquise Reed in the final seconds of the game.
videos.headline: Brissett rejects potential game-tying basket
